    "3D-CNN model to learn spatiotemporal features would be optimal, which is impossible with 2D CNN.",
    "But, because it requires many parameters and a high amount of computation, the 3D model cannot be used to construct deep models 15.",
    "Although transformer architecture dominates natural language processing, its use in medical imaging has been limited 19.",
    "However, Vision Transformer (ViT) has recently gained popularity due to its impressive results in various medical imaging tasks, including image classification, object detection, and semantic segmentation 20.",
